text: Rendezvous with Annie is a 1946 American comedy movie directed by Allan Dwan and starring Eddie Albert, Faye Marlowe, Gail Patrick, C. Aubrey Smith, Raymond Walburn, George Chandler, William Frawley, Joyce Compton. It was distributed by Republic Pictures. ==Other websites== * Category:1946 comedy movies Category:American comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Allan Dwan
title: Rendezvous with Annie
